               <ul class="text-xs space-y-2 list-disc pl-4 opacity-80">
                 <li><strong><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multiprotocol_Label_Switching" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">MPLS</a> & <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Segment_routing" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">SR</a>:</strong> Label-based traffic engineering.</li>
                 <li><strong><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virtual_Extensible_LAN" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">VXLAN</a>, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Generic_Routing_Encapsulation" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">GRE</a>, & <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Generic_UDP_Encapsulation" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">GUE</a>:</strong> Overlay encapsulation.</li>
                 <li><strong><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Address_Resolution_Protocol" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">ARP</a> & <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VLAN" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">VLAN tags</a>:</strong> Local orchestration.</li>
               </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="cyber-box p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-slate-900/20 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800">
