                 <li><strong><a href="https://grpc.io/" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">gRPC</a> & <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Service_mesh" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">Service Meshes</a>:</strong> Microservice orchestration.</li>
